SELECT COALESCE("DISPLAYNAME", "DISPLAYNAME") AS "DISPLAYNAME", "BADGECOUNT", "GOLDCOUNT", "SILVERCOUNT", "BRONZECOUNT", "POSTCOUNT", "QUESTIONCOUNT", "ANSWERCOUNT", "TOTALSCORE", "AVGVIEWCOUNT"
FROM (SELECT "t1"."USERID", "t1"."DISPLAYNAME", "t1"."BADGECOUNT", "t1"."GOLDCOUNT", "t1"."SILVERCOUNT", "t1"."BRONZECOUNT", "t3"."POSTCOUNT", "t3"."QUESTIONCOUNT", "t3"."ANSWERCOUNT", "t3"."TOTALSCORE", "t3"."AVGVIEWCOUNT"
FROM (SELECT ANY_VALUE("Users"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", COUNT("Badges"."Id") AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "GOLDCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "SILVERCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Badges"."Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "BRONZECOUNT"
FROM "STACK"."Users"
LEFT JOIN "STACK"."Badges" ON "Users"."Id" = "Badges"."UserId"
GROUP BY "Users"."Id", "Users"."DisplayName") AS "t1"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "OwnerUserId" AS "OWNERUSERID", COUNT(*) AS "POSTCOUNT", COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", COUNT(CASE WHEN CAST("PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS "ANSWERCOUNT", SUM("Score") AS "TOTALSCORE", AVG("ViewCount") AS "AVGVIEWCOUNT"
FROM "STACK"."Posts"
GROUP BY "OwnerUserId") AS "t3" ON "t1"."USERID" = "t3"."OWNERUSERID") AS "t4"
WHERE "t4"."BADGECOUNT" > 0